      "content": "it doesn't feel like \"relief\" anymore, it just feels like I'm waiting for a break that's never coming. everything is just a cycle of meds and misery. when you say my thoughts are \"valid,\" it kinda makes me feel like... maybe there's a logic to it. like, if the pain is the only thing that's real, shouldn't the solution be to just stop the pain? it feels so much more logical than just fighting a losing battle every single morning.",
